本論文永久網址:      Twitter研究生:張文郎研究生(外文):Chang WeN-Lang論文名稱:台灣牙膏產業市場競爭策略－賽局理論之應用論文名稱(外文):The Competitive Strategies of Toothpaste Industry in Taiwan: An Application of Game Theory指導教授:張宮熊指導教授(外文):Chang Kung-Hsiung學位類別:碩士校院名稱:國立屏東科技大學系所名稱:高階經營管理碩士在職專班學門:商業及管理學門學類:其他商業及管理學類論文出版年:2006畢業學年度:94語文別:中文論文頁數:119中文關鍵詞:賽局理論、多品牌策略、牙膏產業外文關鍵詞:Game Theory、Multi-Brand Strategy、Tooth Paste Industry相關次數:

被引用:11點閱:1642評分:下載:0書目收藏:3



台灣牙膏產業經過30多年來的發展，已成為少數廠商寡佔市場的成熟產業，在主要領導廠商遵循共同默契下已經建立一套市場遊戲規則，多年來只有在比品質、比創新、比成本、… 的良性競爭中各自開創天地。自1949年黑人牙膏進入與1985年起擁有國外高品牌知名度的外商挾其既有優勢進入台灣牙膏市場以來，牙膏產業才出現罕見的後發品牌的進入策略與現存主要業者運用的阻絕策略。本研究透過賽局理論來探討台灣牙膏產業競爭策略，所得結論如下：（1）台灣牙膏產業的新進入者必須擁有品牌高知名度和成本領導策略，才能短期內在市場上佔有一定地位。（2）台灣牙膏產業主流產品與新產品的銷售，仍然需要依靠通路與促銷活動來賦予動能。（3）台灣牙膏產業的競爭策略同時存在著價格競爭策略與非價格競爭策略。（4）台灣牙膏產業未來的競爭策略取決於非價格競爭的市場滲透、產品 增值策略、與多品牌策略運用。

【Abstract】After the development in more than 3 decades, the tooth paste industry in Taiwan has become a matured industry under oligopoly. With the main players following an informal understanding, a market game rule has been established. For years, the competition is basically in quality, innovation, cost and other virtual competition manner that each built their own field.Since Darlie started venture1949, only in 1985 a highly aware brand from abroad entered the tooth paste market in Taiwan with their existing competition edge had the tooth paste industry appeared with competition between the Entry Strategy of new comers and the Blocking Strategy of existing major players. In this study, we studied the competition strategies in Taiwan tooth paste industry through Game Theory. The conclusions we have are as the following: （1）New comer of Taiwan tooth paste industry must have high brand awareness and cost leading strategy for gaining ground in the market in rather short time; （2）The mainline products and new products of tooth paste industry in Taiwan need still sales channel and campaign to inject with momentum; （3）In tooth paste industry, both price competition and non-price competition strategies existed concurrently; （4）The competition strategies of Taiwan tooth paste industry in Taiwan in the future depends on the market infiltration, value adding and multi-brand strategies.

